  "materials_text": "",
  "steps": [
    "1 mL of 4 µg/mL Sudan black B solution is added to the funnel and is drawn through the filter at a vacuum pressure of -70 kPa.",
    "Suction is applied until the PCTE filter appears dry. The flow rate through 30 nm pore PCTE filters is approximately 0.1 mL/min, at -70 kPa using a 25mm diameter funnel."
  ],
